### Importacion

```{r}
data <- read_csv('Data/WA_Fn-UseC_-Telco-Customer-Churn.csv')
```

#### Verificar y corregir columnas

```{r}
data %>% glimpse
```

```{r}
data %>% 
  mutate(
    SeniorCitizen= factor(SeniorCitizen, levels= c(0, 1), 
                             labels= c('no', 'si') )
  ) ->
  data
```

